OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with patchy rain at
OL,6,Ffirst and again during the afternoon.
OL,7,FOutbreaks of rain, heaviest over
OL,8,FDumfries and Galloway, spread
OL,9,Fnortheast for a time in the morning.
OL,10,FBecoming windy in the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe night will continue
OL,13,Fcloudy and mild with further outbreaks
OL,14,Fof rain, this becoming heavy at times
OL,15,Fover the hills. Windy.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FEarly rain will clear east as
OL,18,Fthe wind falls light in the morning.
OL,19,FSunny spells will increase before
OL,20,Fshowers spread into the west from late
OL,21,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
